Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.Settings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains static methods that can be called to get global Settings to be used throughout the codebase.
